title: Microsoft Surface Pro 9
description: Microsoft Surface Pro 9 SQ3 WIFI+5G 16GB RAM 512GB SSD 13 Multi-Touch Laptop for Business (RZ1-00001) The Microsoft Surface Pro 9 SQ3 Touch Laptop for Business (RZ1-00001) is a high-performance computing device tailored for professional use, offering a powerful set of features in a portable form factor. Running on Windows 11 Pro, it is equipped with the Microsoft SQ3 processor and boasts a substantial 16GB LPDDR4x memory and capacious 512GB SSD storage, ensuring robust performance and ample space for your work-related data. The Microsoft Surface Pro 9 laptop features a 13 2880x1920 multi-touch display with a high refresh rate of 120 Hz, delivering vibrant visuals and smooth touch interactions. It also incorporates facial recognition for enhanced security and convenience. With a sleek and compact design, this laptop is equipped with two Thunderbolt 4-enabled USB-C ports for versatile connectivity. It supports Wi-Fi 6E (802.11ax) with tri-band support for high-speed wireless connections and Bluetooth 5.1. One unique feature is its 4G LTE support via a Nano-SIM, with compatibility across various bands for connectivity on the go. It also supports multiple GNSS systems, including BeiDou, GLONASS, GPS, and Galileo. The laptop has a rear camera system with a 10 MP sensor for capturing high-quality images and UHD 4K video recording. Its long-lasting 47.7 Wh battery offers an estimated battery life of up to 15.5 hours, ensuring you can work all day without interruption. The Microsoft Surface Pro 9 laptop's compact dimensions of 11.3 x 8.2 x 0.4 (287 x 209 x 9.3 mm) and lightweight profile of 1.9 lb (883 g) make it an ideal choice for professionals on the move, combining power, portability, and security in one sleek package.
